    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sailor's rhythmic songs, especially those sung while undertaking labor aboard ship; for example, shanties may be sung when a group is manipulating heavy sails by means of ropes. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
